replies.body:
I have a few moments C;

1. When Peachy told me I passed my Jr Mod trial at 5:30 in the morning.
2. When I went to my first staff meeting, Michael was soooooo funny xD
3. When I scrimmed with Apollo, they're an amazing team.

My favourite Minecraft moment as a whole was on my previous server, we connected with Para's old server and they had the Equinox gamemode (DTM), I played a map called 'Giants Causeway', lasted 6 hours. :)
